Application Business Requirements

User:
•	Ability to upload purchase order confirmation, picture of item that needs to be picked up 
•	Ability to set a time and a location when item is purchased and ready for delivery (maximum day delivery, max location)
•	Ability to review drivers
•	Ability to tip the driver
•	Ability for the user to check estimated time delivery and driver’s live location.(Google Maps Integration)
•	Ability to chat with User



Driver:
•	Ability to turn online or offline for delivery.
•	Ability to accept or decline a delivery request
•	Ability to use a GPS within the application. (Google Maps Integration)
•	Ability to review customer.
•	Ability to chat with User, or Phone call



 
